<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: ate awful sausage -->
  <SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_awful_sausage.label>끔찍한 소시지를 먹음</SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_awful_sausage.label>
  <!-- EN: I ate a mixture of raw meat with salt grains that could barely be called a sausage. Completely disgusting. -->
  <SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_awful_sausage.description>소시지라고 간신히 부를만한 생고기와 소금 혼합물을 먹었어. 완전 역겨워.</SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_awful_sausage.description>
  <!-- EN: ate poor sausage -->
  <SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_poor_sausage.label>나쁜 소시지를 먹음</SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_poor_sausage.label>
  <!-- EN: That sausage was a little humid to be completely mature, I could still feel the flavour of raw meat. -->
  <SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_poor_sausage.description>완전히 건조되지 않은 소시지를 먹었어. 날고기 맛이 느껴졌어.</SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_poor_sausage.description>
  <!-- EN: ate normal sausage -->
  <SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_normal_sausage.label>평범한 소시지를 먹음</SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_normal_sausage.label>
  <!-- EN: ate good sausage -->
  <SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_good_sausage.label>좋은 소시지를 먹음</SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_good_sausage.label>
  <!-- EN: I ate a nice and tasty sausage. -->
  <SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_good_sausage.description>괜찮고 맛있는 소시지를 먹었어..</SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_good_sausage.description>
  <!-- EN: ate excellent sausage -->
  <SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_excellent_sausage.label>완벽한 소시지를 먹음</SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_excellent_sausage.label>
  <!-- EN: That sausage was delicious. It's easy to notice it has been well aged. -->
  <SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_excellent_sausage.description>그 소시지는 정말 맛있었어. 잘 숙성된거 같아</SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_excellent_sausage.description>
  <!-- EN: ate masterwork sausage -->
  <SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_masterwork_sausage.label>걸작 소시지를 먹음</SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_masterwork_sausage.label>
  <!-- EN: I experienced a flavour only thought to be felt by the most refined palates! -->
  <SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_masterwork_sausage.description>엄청 호화로운 음식에서 나올법한 맛을 경험했어!</SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_masterwork_sausage.description>
  <!-- EN: ate legendary sausage -->
  <SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_legendary_sausage.label>전설적인 소시지를 먹음</SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_legendary_sausage.label>
  <!-- EN: To be able to taste a food this delicious is something not ordinary! I'm completely pleased! -->
  <SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_legendary_sausage.description>솔직히 말해서, 이 맛은 무언가 보통의 맛이 아니야! 엄청 마음에 들었어!</SM_AteSausage.stages.ate_legendary_sausage.description>
  
</LanguageData>